\par }{\f4\cgrid0 To use }{\i\f4\cgrid0 SimCity 3000}{\f4\cgrid0 , you and your students will need the following basic computer skills:
\par 
\par }\pard \fi-240\li720\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\f4\cgrid0 \bullet \tab Starting an application
\par 
\par \bullet \tab Using a mouse
\par 
\par \bullet \tab Using menus and submenus
\par 
\par \bullet \tab Clicking and dragging
\par 
\par \bullet \tab Saving and loading files to a floppy or hard disk
