\par }\pard \fi-240\li240\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\f4\cgrid0 \bullet \tab Have students devise an experiment to see how fire stations 
(or lack thereof) affect the chance of fires within a city. After students devise their tests, have them test their predictions using }{\i\f4\cgrid0 SimCity 3000}{\f4\cgrid0 
. Remind students that in order for fires to occur in the program, the disasters setting must first be turned on.
\par }\pard \nowidctlpar\adjustright {\f17\fs24\cgrid0 
\par }{\b\f4\fs28\cgrid0 Simulation 4: SIMS Just Want To Have Fun!
