\par }{\b\f4\fs24\cgrid0 Objectives
\par }{\f4\cgrid0 
\par }\pard \fi-240\li720\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\f4\cgrid0 \bullet \tab To observe how recreational and cultural facilities affect both the land value of a city and the Sims' well being.
