\par }{\f4\cgrid0 
\par In this simulation, students will compare and contrast the aura 
and land value levels of two cities, one of which contains recreational facilities and services and the other of which doesn't. Students will find that the overall aura (the happiness level of the Sims in a city) and land value levels are higher in the ci
ty that contains recreational facilities and services.
\par 
\par Have students perform the following actions:
