\par 6.\tab Select the }{\b\f4\cgrid0 Land Value Data }{\f4\cgrid0 Map in the }{\b\f4\cgrid0 View Data }{\f4\cgrid0 Window. In general, which city has a higher land value, the one with services and recreational facilities or the one without?
