\par }\pard \fi-240\li240\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\f4\cgrid0 \bullet \tab 
Have students research the different residential and cultural facilities in their area. Create a class list of the different items. Then ask the class to rank the items in order of desirability. Which types of facilities were the most desirable?
 Why? Which were the least desirable? Why?
